plot outline: Karthik is a software engineer who falls in love with Harika. Even though Harika hates Karthik at first, she falls in love with him during the course of time. When the couple decides to marry each other, Prince (Noel Sean) enters the scene and challenges to Karthik that he will break his love affair and marry Harika at any cost.
